[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "みんな、いらっしゃい！\n第２回九偉人会に向けた作戦会議を開始するわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01236",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "少し前にも聞いた流れですね……\nヴァレリア、この会議の目的について説明を求めます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01237",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "目的はズバリ、料理を作ってヘルトに振る舞おう！\n料理は私たちみんなで作ろう！　ってところね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01238",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ、だからヘルト兄貴はいないんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01239",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ご飯を食べるのは、前回やってダメだったじゃん。\nまた同じことする以上、考えはあるんだろうね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01240",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "超あるわよ！　料理は私たちみんなで作るのよ。\n恐らくヘルトの好物である……スープを！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01241",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "柔らかい肉と芋が入ったスープじゃ！\nあ、我は食す専門じゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01242",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なに言ってんのよ。\nあんたも調理に参加してもらうんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01243",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様のスープ……\nもしかして、あのスープのことだろうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01244",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "よく特訓の後に作ってくれたスープだよね！\n温かくて、具だくさんのやつ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01245",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "それならば私も食べたことがある。大変、美味",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01246",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アタシもあるよ。というか、\nナナ時代のヴァレリア含め全員食べたことあるはずさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01247",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "へえー、全員！？　\nてことは、いよいよヘルトの好物で決まりじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01248",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "このスープのレシピ、みんな知ってる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01249",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "味から、恐らくこれだろうというレシピは分かります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01250",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヘル兄本人から聞けないんじゃあ、\nアタシたちの記憶の味を頼りにやるっきゃないかね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01251",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "はい！　皆で力を合わせれば、\nきっと兄様のスープを作ることができます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01252",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとうみんな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01253",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "このスープを飲んで、ヘルトが\nいつも通りに戻るなんて思ってないけど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01254",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "少しでも、ヘルトの心に\n私たちの気持ちが届けばいいなって思うのよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01255",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私たちの、気持ち？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01256",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。みんながヘルトをどう思っているかは\nそれぞれだろうし、分からないけれど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01257",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私はみんなから話を聞いて、ヘルトってやっぱり\n私たちのお兄ちゃんなんだなって思ったのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01258",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "それが、ナナがヘルト兄様に伝えたい気持ちなんだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01259",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。ちっぽけかもしれないけれど、\n兄弟として、家族として、ヘルトを支えたいなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01260",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "いいねぇ、いいねぇ！　粋だねぇ！\nよーし、みんなでうまいスープを作ろうじゃないか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01261",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "諾。力仕事はお任せください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01262",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕はまだやるなんて言ってないんだけど……\nまぁ、これまでの恨みつらみでも込めてやろうかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01263",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者のスープを一番食しているのは我じゃからな、\n味見は任せい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01264",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ゼロ姉様に試食を任せたら、鍋が空になります。\n……鍋には近づかせません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01265",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私も精一杯手伝うよ！\n頑張ろうね、ヴァレリア姉ちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01266",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ！　兄弟みんなで頑張るわよ！\nおー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01267",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]